Description: Fragment of rim of Baetican pottery transport amphora, type Dressel 20. Clay medium-fine buff; light grey core. Rectangular stamp on outside of rim.
Curator's comments: Trimmed. Published by Elizabeth Lyding Will, 'Exportation of olive oil from Baetica to the Eastern Mediterranean', in Blasquez, J, (ed), Producción y comercio del aceite en la antigüedad : Segundo Congreso Internacional : Sevilla, 24-28 febrero 1982, Madrid 1983, 395, no. 3.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.1261)
